factsheet.heading: The Walk
paragraphs: Step back in time to 16th century, discover the secrets, spies and stories that give this walk the title it deserves.

This walk 100, 200, 300 years ago would tell a completely different story, we will cover 500 years in less than 2 hours. As well as the magnificent gems you see, we reveal buildings that are not what they appear to be ...

On this walk what you see is not always what it seems. Victoria is very much past, present and future.  The past is preserved, they are currently undergoing huge developments ready for a thriving future. We cannot predict the future, but we can and love to reveal the past.

name: Secret Victoria, Westminster
